data.description: Owner Occupied, please no trespassing without an appointment. This welcoming property offers a serene retreat in the heart of nature. Built in 2022 and recently cleared lot, this home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for your family's comfort. Step inside and be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The spacious island in the kitchen offers plenty of room for meal preparation and serving. The primary suite is complete with a en-suite bath, double vanity and walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and can be customized to fit your lifestyle. Outside, you'll find a sprawling 1-acre lot, allowing you to embrace the natural beauty that surrounds you. Additionally, the property boasts a 1,260 sq ft shop. Take advantage of the nearby recreational opportunities, including hiking, fishing, and exploring the beautiful trails in the area. Schedule your private tour today! 2023-11-03
